text: Oriana Bedingfield (born 6 July 1984) is a Maltese footballer who plays as a midfielder for First Division club Mosta FC. She has been a member of the Malta women's national team. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Mosta F.C. players
